RAW kicks off with Rollins, McIntyre, and Punk in the ring. McIntyre says he won't stop until Punk's heart does. Rollins wants them both to know that what HE says goes.

McIntyre mocks Punk knowing they can't touch each other

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5558ae10-d560-4e11-a427-284c98b70a7c/20240729_173936.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_CREED BROS DEF. OTIS AND TOZAWA_**
    

Maxxine stops Gable and the Creed Bros from jumping Otis and she's willing to fight off all three men.

But she won't have to because the Wyatt6 is here!!! THEY FINALLY UNMASK!

Joe Gacy, Erick Rowan, and Dexter Lumis get in the ring and Gable leave the Creed Bros to get attacked.

Gacy powerbombs Dexter Lumis ONTONthe Creed Bros and Uncle Howdy comes out to cut Gable off at the entrance way to end the segment.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1125c977-97e1-4150-836f-28c571f478e5/20240729_180552.jpg?format=original)

BRONSON REED DEF. SHEAMUS

Pete Dunne ran in when the ref was not looking and clocked Sheamus with a sheleighly to allow Bronson to get the win.

Good match.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fc5d7a8e-3b07-48bd-bd21-1de6c36c01cc/Screenshot_20240729_182719.jpg?format=original)

JEY USO DEF CARLITO

Earlier in the night the Judgement Day found their clubhouse burnt down and the PS5 destroyed. Rhea says it can only be Liv but Carlito wanted to know if she was going to replace the PlayStation.

Rhea is pissed and forced him to fight Jey Uso tonight.. alone. Carlito loses the match after Jey Uso spears the apples out of Carlito’s mouth

